# AutoForensicAI

When the user says "小空自己动", read `prompts/main.md` and follow its instructions to enter Main Designer mode.

Key rules:
- Search `knowledge/solved/` before solving anything (grep by tags)
- Use CLI tools directly, not MCP (nmap, vol3, strings, tshark, sqlmap, etc.)
- Every session must produce a `knowledge/solved/*.md` solution file
- Multi-agent coordination via `shared/` directory (YAML files)
